{
  "stem": "13623.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew they were being taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were people from other towns that were taken someplace, but we didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We found out later that they were taken over the border to, to the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When they arrived in the Ukraine, they were mass-executed, and they were buried in mass graves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We did not know that at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When this-- one of the guys that was drafted into this labor battalion, one of the Jewish guys, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Mechel ?] Steimetz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was in the Ukraine, and he came home and told people about what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "None of us believed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Life is going on in the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The new--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not me personally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a kid of 12, 13 at the time, but he was telling the adults and I heard adults talking about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That people actually thought that this man was out of his mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not believe that people would just kill in cold blood and execute people and just bury them in a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People just didn't want to believe that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was still going to school and to cheder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A new order came out from, from the what we called the feathers, the police, that all males 12 years and up have to one day a week report to the police station.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at the police station we had to wear yellow arm bands, and we would made-- we were given picks and shovels, and we were made to work labor on the highway department, different work, whether they needed it or not, just a form of harassing.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was one day a week that we had to report.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
